\newlabel{tab:supp-downstream-pipeline}{{4}{3}{Decisive downstream pipeline experiment, $24$ trials. Pipeline = raw $\to $ \texttt {cd-sched} legalizer (5000 SGD steps) vs.\^^Mraw $\to $ VSR-post($\lambda {=}8$) $\to $ \texttt {cd-sched}. $\Delta v\,\%$ is the residual violation count change relative to the raw draft; $\Delta h_m\,\%$ is macros-only HPWL change; $\Delta h_f\,\%$ is full-design HPWL change with cells at \texttt {.pl}; $t$ is total wall-clock. Raw rows: \texttt {results/vsr\_extra/round2\_review.json}}{table.4}{}}
